      "updated": 1775599429479,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For parsing the OSM fiel there's a c++\nlibrary called osmium that will simplify\nthis a lot: \nhttps://osmcode.org/libosmium/manual.\nhtml",
